{"word":"σπουδάζω","slug":"σπουδάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>σπουδάζω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:σπουδή\">σπουδή</a></el>] ‘make a strong effort’, <b>strive<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of movement to a place <b><a href='B:620 4:9'>2 Ti 4:9</a>, <a href='B:620 4:21'>21</a>; <a href='B:630 3:12'>Tit 3:12</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ transf.\">transf.</a> sense, of eagerness to carry out an obligation or achieve an objective (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> our ‘go out of one’s way’) <b><a href='B:550 2:10'>Gal 2:10</a>; <a href='B:560 4:3'>Eph 4:3</a>; <a href='B:590 2:17'>1 Th 2:17</a>; <a href='B:620 2:15'>2 Ti 2:15</a>; <a href='B:650 4:11'>Hb 4:11</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:σπόρος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:σπουδαῖος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}